snippet: Rory McIlroy birdied three of his final four holes, and had an eagle, five birdies and two bogeys to match his lowest PGA Tour round this year.
abstract: Rory McIlroy takes second-round lead at St Jude Classic golf tournament, snapping his string of three straight missed cuts.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy birdied three of his final four holes, and had an eagle, five birdies and two bogeys to match his lowest PGA Tour round this year.

headline.seo: McIlroy Shoots 5-Under 65 to Take Lead at St. Jude Classic
headline.main: McIlroy Shoots 5-Under 65 to Take Lead at St. Jude Classic
